\par The behavior of this function is undefined if copying takes place between objects that overlap--for example, if \i ws\i0  is also given as an argument to receive a string read under control of the `\f3 %s\f0 ', `\f3 %S\f0 ', or `\f3 %[\f0 ' conversion.
