\par 
\par \pard\li500 The value of this macro is an integer constant representing the largest value the \f3 rand\f0  function can return. In t\f1 his \f0 librar\f1 y\f0 , it\f1  is 32767.  In other libraries it may be higher.\f0 
\par 
\par \pard -- Function: int \b rand\b0  (\i void\i0 )
\par 
